班不連願對<br />\n吳思遠話成個電影界都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n金融管理專員過去5年共收到265宗複製香港流通紙幣的申請，5宗不獲批准、10宗涉及申請人放棄申請，其餘250宗均獲專員書面同意；絕大多數是用作製作教科書、廣告、電視或電影項目，個案不獲批原因包括複製的貨幣非香港流通紙幣等。一般而言，專員會在收到申請後7個工作天內回覆申請人，並於約兩周內完成審批。"},{"pid":"4cfea44709b5b9dc479656576f0967b652a88ccf","tid":685994,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:56:42.000Z","msg":"咁黑警放蛇都係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedffe427b10e06f1931431cbbe741ee7c86f9a0","tid":685994,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:57:31.000Z","msg":"以乲火印左道具兩隻字就得添"},{"pid":"34bfd77cc1fd98592fd1fb8701925f4d11fd18ce","tid":685994,"uid":57023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"原來大狀都有語無倫次既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34dd9684f0889f89342f747c80d3a6ecb22b122d","tid":685994,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:03:52.000Z","msg":"用手cg?<br />\n佢係咪弱智"},{"pid":"a87b4ee95c5c114a75725e0f4988f47a7a8db868","tid":685994,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"條友究竟收左老共幾多錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cb8b4820f18083b4d14e60129fbc4b73da719a","tid":685994,"uid":67302,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"On撚鳩<br />\n咁醫生開刀又係咪要告「普通襲擊罪」？"},{"pid":"a69bec131089ee1c56285f478fec15c53db90f0f","tid":685994,"uid":178619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:09:51.000Z","msg":"其實好地地申請左先咪得，依家佢無申請俾人發現左告佢，咁都有得瀨?"},{"pid":"5837c22adcd0ba44b5b6c8615c3bc004d60bda4c","tid":685994,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:12:11.000Z","msg":"十一哥收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n不過今舖我都唔撐業界"},